# Simple discussion mission for quick demo
# Format: id, pn, pe, h, action, param1, param2, ...
#
# Behavior:
# - Initial entry segment from waypoint 10 to waypoint 20
# - Then a clean rectangular loop: 20 -> 30 -> 40 -> 50 -> 20
# - Returns to waypoint 20 (not the start waypoint 10)
# - No diagonal closure segment, so the top-view path stays clean for discussion

10, 0.0, 0.0, 30.0
20, 0.0, 200.0, 30.0
30, 400.0, 200.0, 30.0
40, 400.0, 400.0, 30.0
50, 0.0, 400.0, 30.0, GO_WAYPOINT, 20
